---+++ Status Report from the OSG Executive Director, OSG Project Manager and/or Others

   * OSG Executive Director's Report (XD News?) [[https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Council/EdReport-Apr13-2010][Executive Report]]
   * OSG Project Manager Report [[https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/twiki/pub/Council/Agenda2010Mar11/OSG_Satellites_Proposal_11mar2010.pptx][OSG Interface to Satellite Proposals/Projects]]
   * OSG Usage by Science Domain (Jim Weichel); see [[https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Trash/Trash/Trash/Trash/MeasurementsAndMetrics/MetricScienceUsage][Metric for Non HEP Science Usage of the OSG]]
