---+++ Round-Table Virtual Organization Reports and Issues:

%BLUE% *minutes:*

Brad Abbott (D0): Everything is running smoothly for D0 with no major issues. MC production has been roughly constant of 10 million events/day from OSG.  Now that we have LCG running (thanks to OSG) we are getting ~ 4 million events/week from LCG.

Tom Furlani (Collective VOs): Collective VO Representatives need a better way to to collect information from stakeholders. The weekly meetings held by Abhishek are focused on current technical challenges and not giving a strategic look at the needs and feedback for planning for the future. A suggestion to have a monthly meeting with leadership was made by Tom. Abhishek said he would be willing to meet with Tom and Shaowen on a monthly bases to give a synthesized few from the "field". This may need further inputs from VO leadership. Abhishek reported that he has held these types of meetings in the past. Abhishek provided this [[https://twiki.grid.iu.edu/bin/view/Trash/Trash/Trash/Trash/VirtualOrganizations/SummarytoCouncil_04132010 ][link]] to a quarterly summary.

